- Must-haves match (0â€“40)  
- Relevant experience depth & recency (0â€“25)  
- Evidence/impact (metrics, outcomes) (0â€“15)  
- Role level fit (0â€“10)  
- Nice-to-haves (0â€“10)  

If CVs are very similar, break ties using:  

- Clearer evidence of impact  
- Closer domain fit  
- More recent relevant work  
